    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lofirunner is a fast, 3D platformer with toon artstyle and versatile movement ranging from wallrunning to dashing. Race against time in different levels while avoiding obstacles. Challenge yourself with the hardest time medals that require vast knowledge of the game's movement.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty of Levels</strong><br>10 Levels at launch</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Versatile Movement</strong><br>Utilize grapple, dashing, sliding and more to reach the best times.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>True Challenge</strong><br>Challenge your self with hard time medals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Toon Artstyle</strong><br>Enjoy different colorful enviroments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Achievements</strong><br>Challenge yourself.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Music</strong><br>Amazing soundtrack, made by <strong>Tuomas Lehtonen.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
